Booo!
v0.1.6 ~ October 30, 2024

Scared you, didn't we? Not as much as the new Scythe, the first new melee weapon in SUPREM.IO's history, which deals a crushing blow to all enemies around you! So put on the new Pumpkin Head and get to slashing!

Join SUPREM.IO's Discord Server to participate in the upcoming Topaz Tournament for a chance to win some Discord Nitro!

Ninjas & Shurikens!
v0.1.5 ~ July 30, 2024

SUPREM.IO now has server selection, with new servers in Europe and Asia!

This update also adds the Shuriken, a fast-flying throwable, and the Ninja Mask.

Don't forget to join SUPREM.IO's Discord Server to tell us your thoughts about the new update!

SUPREM on the Go!
v0.1.4 ~ June 16, 2024

This update brings SUPREM.IO to mobile! You can now play anywhere, from your couch to your commute. Mobile is still in beta, so please report any bugs on SUPREM.IO's Discord Server.

This update also includes a Minigun nerf, reducing its bullet spread considerably for better balance on open maps.

We also bring some quality of life updates: you can now swap weapons with one click, and weapon pickups are more consistent. Enjoy!

One on One
v0.1.3 ~ May 26, 2024

This update brings a 1v1 Duel lobby! Duel a random opponent in a 1v1 match, wearing the new Paper Bag hat!

This update also brings some changes to abilities: Upsurge now jumps a bit lower, and Wallbreaker reduces knockback when activated.

If you still haven't done so, join SUPREM.IO's Discord Server to discuss this new update, find people to play with, and have an amazing time!

SUPREM.IO Discord
Impel
Propel horizontally, becoming invulnerable for 0.15 seconds.
Cooldown: 10s
Upsurge
Thrust up into the air, thrust down if holding the Move Down key.
Cooldown: 10s
Wallbreaker
Ignite your hands, increasing the range and power (enough to break blocks!) of your next fist punch, also increasing movement speed for 2.5 seconds.
Cooldown: 10s
